        <span class="stat-num">约 6,400<small>&nbsp;亿美元</small></span>
        <span class="stat-label">美国四大 hyperscaler 2026 资本开支；芯片不缺，缺的是电</span>
      </div>

      <div class="stat" data-lang="en">
        <span class="stat-num">4–5<small>&nbsp;×</small></span>
        <span class="stat-label">Huawei Ascend logic capacity vs HBM-limited output (2025); power isn't the binding constraint here</span>
      </div>
